description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Control Your Legs Row' from the channel Laine Karwoski.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
